    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Your ranged attacks ignore anything but total concealment and cover.</em><br /><br /><strong>Prerequisites</strong><br />Dex 19, Point-Blank Shot, Precise Shot, base attack bonus +11.<br /><br /><strong>Benefits</strong><br />Your ranged attacks ignore the AC bonus granted to targets by anything less than total cover, and the miss chance granted to targets by anything less than total concealment. Total cover and total concealment provide their normal benefits against your ranged attacks.<br /><br /><strong>Normal</strong><br />See the normal rules on the effects of cover and concealment in Combat.<br /><br /><strong>Combat Trick</strong><br />When you use the ability of the Precise Shot combat trick, the bonuses increase to +4.</p>",
